[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     69[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mBedrock invocation in Step 7 correctly carries [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mtemperature = 0.0[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (deterministic-ish output), constructs prompts with structured context (the user's identity context, the patient's encounter context, the access event detail, prior cases, the relationship-graph view), and the closing framing "Decision support, not decision-making" matches the chapter-3-settled discipline.[K
