[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    121[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mFor a system that informs privacy-office investigations, HR employment actions, and HIPAA breach-notification decisions, blast-radius minimization matters: a compromised role with broad case-state-write access could silently corrupt case state (mark a case as dismissed when it wasn't, link a case to the wrong workforce member, suppress an open case), which would propagate into wrong investigation decisions, wrong HR referrals, and wrong breach-notification timing. A compromised role with broad workforce-identity-read access exposes the rolling identity of every workforce member, including their role, department, manager, schedule, hire date, address ZIP, and last name (the demographic data that drives same-name and same-address detection).[K
