[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    167[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThe recipe-3.9-distinctive amplification: the LLM narrative in this recipe will inform an investigator's decision that may lead to an HR employment action and a HIPAA breach notification. The narrative's accuracy and the constraint discipline are part of the labor-and-legal defense; an LLM that asserts intent or violation is producing evidence that the investigator does not have the authority to validate. The constraint discipline matters more here than in clinical-decision-support contexts.[K
