[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    629[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    630[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThe recipe correctly identifies this concern in the Bedrock paragraph framing ("the LLM is producing decision support, not decisions") and in The Honest Take ("Always with human review; the LLM produces decision support, not decisions"), but the sample narrative includes a near-routing-recommendation. A reader implementing the explanation layer who uses the sample as a template will produce narratives that drift toward operational recommendations rather than pattern descriptions.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    631[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
